---
title: Silent Key Tributes
override:tags:
  - about
layout: page
aliases:
- /main/sk
pagination:
  data: collections['silent-key']
  reverse: true
  size: 5
---

<p>
<img src="/about/silent-key/sk.jpg" class="sk-photo">
This page is dedicated to honoring the memories of deceased CAARA members. The
members listed **SK** here made diverse and significant contributions to the
Cape Ann Amateur Radio Association which benefited their fellow hams and the
general welfare of the Club. May they Rest In Peace as we preserve the memories
of their camaraderie and service.
</p>

{% for entry in pagination.items %}
{% assign callsign_lower = entry.data.callsign | downcase %}
{% assign photo_jpg = "about/silent-key/" | append: callsign_lower | append: "/cover.jpg" %}
{% assign has_photo = photo_jpg | fileExists %}
<div class="sk-entry{% if entry.data.military %} sk-military{% endif %}">
<h3>{{ entry.data.name }}, {{ entry.data.callsign }}{% if entry.data.date %} ({{ entry.data.date | date: "%Y" }}){% endif %}</h3>
{% if has_photo %}<img src="/about/silent-key/{{ callsign_lower }}/cover.jpg" alt="{{ entry.data.name }}" class="sk-photo">{% endif %}
{{ entry.content }}
</div>
{% endfor %}

{% if pagination.href.previous or pagination.href.next %}
<nav class="pagination-nav" aria-label="Announcements pagination">
  {% if pagination.href.previous %}
  <a class="pagination-newer" href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}">&laquo; Newer</a>
  {% endif %}
  {% if pagination.href.next %}
  <a class="pagination-older" href="{{ pagination.href.next }}">Older &raquo;</a>
  {% endif %}
</nav>
{% endif %}
